name: 01 Enterprise Limited
overview:
01 Enterprise is a privately owned company which develops Email Marketing Management System, Academic Survey System, e-Commerce System and provides IT consulting service to more than 100 organizations in Hong Kong and worldwide.

We pride ourselves on our close relationships with our clients, whose direct feedback helps to shape the function and future innovation of our products. We’re all about providing high quality software and IT service backed by knowledgeable and friendly sales team and customer support.

You’ll be glad to know that we’re always pushing the limits of software technology to make sure our products and services meet your needs and remains the most popular in its class. If you have any feedback about our products or would like more information about 01 Enterprise please contact us.
